This paper deals with deep neural networks for image classification, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the use of quantization and hardware acceleration, which are relevant to machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural networks (cs.NE). Additionally, the paper proposes a novel computation pattern for efficient computing, which could fall under the category of computer architecture (cs.AR).
